## рџ”„ Data Migration Strategy

### Migration Script (Node.js)

```bash
# 1. Export MySQL data
mysqldump slabccco_sciencedb > backup.sql

# 2. Run migration
node scripts/migrate-mysql-to-postgres.js
```

```javascript
// scripts/migrate-mysql-to-postgres.js
// 1. Read from MySQL using mysql2
// 2. Transform and insert into PostgreSQL using Prisma
// Key transforms:
//   - Hash passwords: bcrypt.hashSync(plaintext, 10)
//   - Map role IDs: 1в†’ADMIN, 2в†’STAFF, 3в†’STUDENT, 4в†’TEACHER
//   - Convert batchid to integer
//   - Merge feetbl records into receipts where amount > 100
//   - Fix stddob '0000-00-00' в†’ null
```

